widgets_values:
If you are having Out Of Memory errors in the "WanVideo Animate Embeds" step,  it is probably because your VRAM can't handle the original amount of Frames and resolution all at once. To (maybe) solve it, increase the value in "Divide FWS" by 1 until it fits in VRAM.

← ← ← ← ← ← ← 

If that doesn't work, try the "Divide FWS" method again, but now enable the "tiled_vae" in the "WanVideo Animate Embeds".

If neither methods work you'll have to accept the hardware limitations and decrease the video resolution.

Use the Scheduler that works best for you. LCM has been working fine for me.

Also force offload the models out of Memory if you want.
